This repository contains the files to reproduce the results and figures presented in

A. Attallah and H. Werner,
"An Information Flow Filter Approach to Formation Control for Heterogeneously Scheduled LPV Â Agents", 
submitted to the 60th Conference on Decision and Control, 2021.

The figures can be reproduced using the file 'IFF_Heterogenous.m'.

The code has been tested using:
  - Matlab R2019b
  - yalmip, solver: sdpt3
  
